org.apache.mahout.math.set

Class HashUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.mahout.math.set.HashUtils

  • public final class HashUtils
extends Object
    Computes hashes of primitive values. Providing these as statics allows the templated code to compute hashes of sets.
